videos.headline: Ohio strikes first with 3-yard punch-in
videos.description: Ohio RB Maleek Irons plows through a defender and plunges into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown, completing the 74-yard opening drive.

videos.headline: Miami knots score at 7-7
videos.description: Miami Ohio running back Alonzo Smith takes a handoff right up the gut of the Ohio defense for a 3-yard touchdown on its first drive.

videos.headline: Miami WR climbs ladder for 12-yard TD
videos.description: Miami Ohio quarterback Gus Ragland lobs a fade pass to Luke Mayock in the back of the end zone, who leaps and pulls down the 12-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Miami's Smith muscles in for 2nd TD of half
videos.description: Miami Ohio running back Alonzo Smith takes the handoff and rumbles into the end zone for an 8-yard touchdown, his second of the half.
